documentation_summary: AutoGluon.multimodal version 1.0.0, released on November 30, 2023, is a Python package available on PyPI for automated machine learning (AutoML) applicable to image, text, time series, and tabular data. It simplifies the process of training and deploying high-accuracy machine learning and deep learning models with minimal coding effort. The package requires Python versions 3.8 to 3.11 and is licensed under the Apache Software License (Apache-2.0). It is developed and maintained by the AutoGluon Community and is intended for a wide range of users including developers, educators, and researchers in various industries. The documentation provides comprehensive guides and examples for installation, usage, and contributing to the project.
